<i>noun</i>: 환난 [환ː난], 풍상 [풍상], 폭풍우 [폭풍우], 진통 [진통], 역경 [역꼉], 어려움 [어려움], 시련 [시ː련], 마 [마], 곤궁 [곤ː궁], 고초 [고초], 고생 [고생], 고난 [고난], 개고생 [개ː고생] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>환난 [환ː난]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; adversity; ordeal; suffering</dd><br>
<dd>매우 걱정되고 고통스러운 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An extremely worrying and painful situation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풍상 [풍상]</dt><br>
<dd>1. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>바람과 서리.</dd><br>
<dd>Wind and frost.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hardship</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 세상의 어려움과 고생.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) Difficulties and troubles of life.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭풍우 [폭풍우]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rainstorm</dd><br>
<dd>폭풍이 불면서 세차게 쏟아지는 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Rain pouring strongly in a storm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hardship</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 생활이나 사업에서 고통이나 어려움을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) One’s state of going through trouble or difficulty in life or in business.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진통 [진통]</dt><br>
<dd>1. labor pains; birth pangs</dd><br>
<dd>임산부가 아이를 낳을 때 반복되는 배의 통증.</dd><br>
<dd>A recurrent spasm of pain that is characteristic of childbirth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hardship; difficulty</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어떤 과정에서 생기는 고통과 시련.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) Hardships and difficulties that one goes through in doing something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>역경 [역꼉]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; adversity</dd><br>
<dd>일이 순조롭게 진행되지 않아 매우 어려운 처지나 환경.</dd><br>
<dd>A very difficult situation or circumstance due to the unsatisfactory progress of a certain work.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어려움 [어려움]</dt><br>
<dd>difficulties; trouble; hardship</dd><br>
<dd>힘들거나 괴로운 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A thing that is difficult and painful to do.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>시련 [시ː련]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hardship; ordeal</dd><br>
<dd>힘든 고난이나 고비.</dd><br>
<dd>A difficult and painful situation or crisis.</dd><br>
<dd>2. trial; test</dd><br>
<dd>의지나 사람됨을 알아보기 위해 시험하여 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of testing someone to find out about his/her will or personality.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>마 [마]</dt><br>
<dd>1. barrier; jinx</dd><br>
<dd>일이 잘 되지 않게 방해를 하는 알 수 없는 장애물.</dd><br>
<dd>An unknown obstacle that keeps things from going well.</dd><br>
<dd>2. being evil; being ominous</dd><br>
<dd>기이하거나 안 좋은 일이 자주 일어나는 장소나 때.</dd><br>
<dd>A place or time in which odd or bad things happen frequently.</dd><br>
<dd>3. difficulty; hardship</dd><br>
<dd>이겨 내기 어려운 일이나 상황.</dd><br>
<dd>A thing or situation that is too difficult to overcome.</dd><br>
<dd>4. devil; evil spirit</dd><br>
<dd>못된 귀신. 또는 못된 귀신처럼 나쁜 일을 하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>An evil ghost; or a person who does bad things like an evil ghost.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곤궁 [곤ː궁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. poverty; destitution</dd><br>
<dd>가난하여 궁핍함.</dd><br>
<dd>Being poor and destitute.</dd><br>
<dd>2. distress; hardship; difficulty</dd><br>
<dd>곤란하고 딱한 처지.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in a dangerous or pathetic situation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고초 [고초]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship</dd><br>
<dd>괴로움과 어려움.</dd><br>
<dd>Distress and difficulty.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고생 [고생]</dt><br>
<dd>trouble; hardship</dd><br>
<dd>괴롭거나 어렵고 힘든 일을 겪음. 또는 그런 생활.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's going through sufferings or hardships, or such a life.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고난 [고난]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; trouble; suffering; difficulty; adversity; trial; ordeal</dd><br>
<dd>매우 괴롭고 어려움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or situation which is extremely difficult and painful.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개고생 [개ː고생]</dt><br>
<dd>hardship; trouble; suffering</dd><br>
<dd>아주 심하게 어렵고 힘든 일을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of suffering from a very difficult and hard problem.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>